kdl.prox.app
Class ImportXMLApp

java.lang.Object
  kdl.prox.app.ImportXMLApp

public class ImportXMLApp
extends java.lang.Object

Application that imports an entire database or part of it from an XML file. The twin of ExportXMLApp. See src/xml/prox3db.dtd for the data format.

NB: Requires Xerces2 Java Parser 2.5.0 Release (or better), which must be ahead of the xerces.jar that comes with JDOM in the class path. todo true?

public ImportXMLApp(java.io.File inputFile,

             throws java.lang.Exception
Full-arg constructor. Uses standard (Xerces2) SAX parsing in order to better scale (over DOM) to very large files.

Parameters:
inputFile - ProxDataML (XML) file to import from. see proximity3/src/xml/prox3db.dtd for the data format
noChecks - when set to true, it allows the addition of new objects, links, and attr vals
